Create Graded Page HW / Video Switch pt. 2 51

-       Step 1: Create Graded Page HW / Video Switch pt. 2

-      - Unhide the HW visual and hide the video visual.

-       - Unhide the HW / Video slicer and choose homework and then hide again.

-         - Create a bookmark, rename to Graded HW.





Step 2: Create Action on HW / Video switch

-           - Select the HW image and go to action. Bookmark should be Graded Video.

-          - Hover over image and press Ctrl + Click, this should take you to the Graded Video bookmark.

-          - Now you will select the Video image and go to action. Bookmark should be Graded HW.

-          - Hover over image and press Ctrl + Click, this should take you to the Graded Video bookmark.

-           - Test a couple of times just to make sure it is correct.






How to create power BI bookmark? follow the link

https://insightsoftware.com/blog/how-to-create-a-bookmark-in-power-bi/#:~:text=Go%20to%20the%20Format%20Image,specific%20bookmark%20of%20your%20choice.
